Quick 24 hour trip. Good times in Miami celebrating the CEO and all around great guy @ghazi 💫 I still don’t think he gets the credit he deserves for what he’s done in the music business. He has changed many lives and really cares about the people who work for him and with him. Vibes created by @mshannahkang @mbpevents 🏆🏆🙌🏾
#HappyBirthdayGhazi

node.text: Congratulations to my guy @dixson he’s a silent killer on the mic, with his 🖊, and on the production!  Many great people in our business saw his greatness but we ended up choosing Sony/ATV @sonymusicpub as his new home. I’ve been watching this man grind for a long time. Well deserved on your first of many deals. This picture is perfect because as the kids say the BIG BAG was secured!  Wait till y’all hear his records and all these other records he’s been writing and producing…. Sheesh!! I swaaaaa y’all ain’t ready!!!
